        <updateDate>2022-01-07T19:40:10Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>American Grown Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits the official display of a cut flower or green in any public area of a building of the Executive Office of the President, the Department of State, or the Department of Defense unless it is produced in the United States.</p> <p>The prohibition does not apply to any cut flower or green used by a federal officer or employee for personal display.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
